            <title>[LU-2141] Soft lockup at mount time</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2141</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We saw a Sequoia client soft lockup during filesystem mount time.  The backtraces from the console are in the sequoia_ion_console.txt attachment.&lt;/p&gt;

