                            <comment id="46605" author="morrone" created="Mon, 15 Oct 2012 20:46:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is happening again, which many Sequoia client nodes hanging.  This is a major problem for sequoia.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The soft lockup messages are exactly the same, and the node is completely unresponsive.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
